Find the surface area of the regular hexagonal pyramid.
(Area of hexagon = 1/2pa.)

Perimeter...........
p = 6 * 12
p = 72

Base area...........
B = 1/2pa
B = 1/2(72)(8)
B = 288

Lateral area........
L = 1/2lp
L = 1/2(24)(72)
L = 864

Total surface area..
S = L + B
S = 864 + 288
S = 1152

